name: Verify the fields under filter edits for Renewals

testSteps.description: 1: Verify the fields under filter edits for Renewals ({Reports=Upcoming Renewals})

children.description: Given underwriter is on home page of PAS
And select Reports 'Upcoming Renewals' from Renewals
When user navigates to the filter edits screen

Then below fields should be visible
| Program |
| Market Segment |
| Underwriting Manager |
